<subSubSection pageNumber="399" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="399">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">Note:</emphasis>
In order to prevent 
<taxonomicName authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Cnicus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">Cnicus</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
from becoming the correct name for 
<taxonomicName authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus" sensu="stricto">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">Centaurea</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">
<taxonomicNameLabel sensu="stricto">sensu stricto</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, Greuter &amp; al. (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">Taxon</emphasis>
50: 1201. 2002) successfully proposed the conservation of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">Centaurea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName authority="L." authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Celosia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="paniculata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">C. paniculata</emphasis>
L.
</taxonomicName>
as its conserved type, in place of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="399">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Centaurea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="centaurium">C. centaurium</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
